come before them.

271
00:17:09,547 --> 00:17:11,048
I understand.

272
00:17:11,277 --> 00:17:15,166
I feel the same way for
myself, for both of us.

273
00:17:16,399 --> 00:17:17,900
I was being foolish.

274
00:17:17,901 --> 00:17:19,902
I only wanted to be with you.

275
00:17:20,213 --> 00:17:22,698
