scholarship, of course.

276
00:17:22,723 --> 00:17:23,723
You'll be a great man,

277
00:17:23,748 --> 00:17:26,151
and the whole district
will be proud of you.

278
00:17:26,176 --> 00:17:27,494
You'll have medals.

279
