You don't belong in it.

322
00:20:26,459 --> 00:20:27,960
Oh, I see.

323
00:20:28,008 --> 00:20:30,009
You mean I'm rather
old-fashioned

324
00:20:30,034 --> 00:20:32,036
and romantic, rather.

325
00:20:33,241 --> 00:20:34,617
Yeah.

326
