Drink your milk, Clavdia.

347
00:23:31,900 --> 00:23:34,903
You will now find it more
comfortable to get up.

348
00:23:37,306 --> 00:23:38,757
Goodbye, Father.

349
00:23:38,766 --> 00:23:41,118
Goodbye, goodbye, goodbye.

350
00:23:41,143 --> 00:23:44,032
